Package: DNCIT
Title: Deep Nonparametric Conditional Independence Test for Images
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Marco", "Simnacher", email="marco.simnacher@hu-berlin.de", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph", "fnd"))
Description: Modular framework for a conditional independence test (CIT) 
            based on a user-given embedding map of the image and the application of
            existing nonparametric CITs to the feature representation 
            of the image and a scalar, given vector-valued c onfounders. 
